===Noun===
'''OR'''
# Logic function OR, true if one or more of inputs are true.  More exactly said ''[[inclusive]] OR'' (as difference from exclusive OR, [[XOR]]).  Denoted in mathematics as <math>\or</math>.

*(0 OR 0) = 0
*(0 OR 1) = 1
*(1 OR 0) = 1
*(1 OR 1) = 1

====Translations====

